  the audio PID.  With SeaChange slicing, it worked the first time, but got
  timeout in the subsequent splice request.

  BUG: seems once the MUX dies, it will keep on dying in the future Apply.
  We have to do a reset to fix the problem. 

  BUG: Found another bug in splicer.c for JinChurn.

  Created view ytse-pcr for PCR's work.


