6/12/00
  Wayne found the bug which causes Harmonic source to die in rate conversion.
  It is in copyPesEsHdr().  In the test of whether the current TP contains
  the fist slice start code, I compute the first slice start code offset
  based on the PES payload start location, instead of from the TP header!

  MUX not responding problem: after MUX dies once, there is no way to restart
  the box without hardware reset.  Always get MUX not responding message
  from the browser.


