  Another bug contributing to the Harmonic source rate conversion problem is
  in the conflict in the definitions of getOffset() and getPesPyldLoc().
  The former is measure from tpPayload, which the latter from tpHdr!
  A difference of 4 bytes needs to be conpensated.

