6/27/00
  Rate control tunning:
    Modified overshoot parameter
      1024 (100%): 1015a - can see beat, occasion skip pictures
      0: 1015b - more blocking, less obvious beat, worse than a.
      512 (50%): beat not observable.  Almost no blocking seen!  No skip pic!

  New splice algorithm:
    To simply things, we no long support pending PTS picture.
    A picture whose PTS cannot be determined will be estimated using
    the no repeated frame/field assumption.

  To do:
    PTS estimation and checking


